      "description": "This used car is in mint condition. The exterior is essentially flawless, with no visible scratches, dents, or paint fade. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and all surfaces are clean and undamaged. Mechanically, the car runs and performs as expected for a vehicle in this condition. All features and systems function properly.",
