    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Value, Solid Ride \u2013 A Car You Can Count On! \ud83d\ude97 Looking for a dependable everyday driver without breaking the bank? This one delivers! This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it runs well, has been reasonably maintained, and presents nicely inside and out. You'll find the usual signs of normal use, but nothing that gets in the way of a comfortable, reliable driving experience. No hidden surprises here \u2014 just a solid car at a fair, transparent price. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are straight and true. The interior is equally impressive, with pristine upholstery, spotless carpets, and all controls and features functioning exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service records are available and confirm consistent, proper maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. This is a rare opportunity to own a used car that genuinely looks and drives like new \u2014 ideal for a buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride that gets the job done? Here's a solid option worth considering! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's mechanically functional and ready to drive, but does show its age with visible wear on the exterior and interior that you'd expect from a well-used car. Some areas may benefit from attention down the road, making this a great pick for a practical buyer who doesn't mind a little TLC. Priced honestly to reflect its condition \u2014 come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A solid opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer looking for a functional, drivable vehicle! This car runs and gets you where you need to go reliably day-to-day. We won't sugarcoat it \u2014 the exterior shows visible wear including some scratches and minor cosmetic blemishes, and the interior reflects its years of use with some noticeable wear on the seats and trim. Mechanically it's in working order, making it a practical choice for someone who needs dependable transportation without the premium price tag. A great starter car or second vehicle at an honest, fair price!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a solid, well-maintained car that has been driven and cared for responsibly over its lifetime. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing modest signs of everyday use such as light wear on the seat fabric and minor scuffs on trim pieces, but nothing that detracts from the overall experience. Mechanically, this car runs reliably and confidently \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are in proper working order. It has been serviced regularly and is ready for daily driving without the need for immediate repairs. This is an honest, dependable vehicle that offers real value for a buyer looking for quality without paying a mint-condition premium.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced accordingly. It is mechanically functional and can be driven, but buyers should be fully aware of its significant shortcomings before purchasing. The exterior has sustained considerable damage, including multiple deep scratches, several dents of varying sizes, and paint that is faded, chipped, and peeling in places. There is visible rust on portions of the body panels. The interior is heavily worn, with torn and stained upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and various trim pieces that are broken or missing. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention, including rough idling, some transmission hesitation, and brakes that are due for replacement. Several warning lights are active on the dashboard. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, needs basic transportation on a tight budget, or is looking for a project car. No warranty is offered, and the car is sold strictly as-is. Please inspect thoroughly before purchase.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    }
